abstract.text: Constants used to add metadata to objects stored in HealthKit.

inlineContent.text: Use these keys to facilitate sharing data between apps. You can also create your own custom keys to give HealthKit objects additional app-specific data.

abstract.text: Access and share health and fitness data while maintaining the user’s privacy and control.
